data.description: Priced to sell ! Adjustment made on this turn key beautiful home that oozes pride of ownership throughout. Built in 2021, this unique floorplan that has been meticulously maintained and ready for a family to enjoy. This 4 bedroom 3 full bath, 3 car garage + bonus room, One story on a corner property has over $110k in tastefully added modern upgrades. High ceilings, tile flooring throughout the home, an open concept floorplan with an ample flowing kitchen perfect for entertaining friends and family, huge quartz kitchen island and countertops, 42' cabinets, smart LED ambient lighting all over, Stainless steel and top of the line appliances. Have to appreciate the custom wall designs along with a custom built entertainment center with TV and high end sound system. Huge master bedroom with 2 spacious walk-in closets, oversized shower, naturally bright double vanity in bathroom. Spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets. Backyard is perfect for those florida days or nights you want to relax or even entertain with a Custom 50x11 screened in covered lanai with pavers, a summer kitchen to thrown down a perfect backyard BBQ, stone counters, TV and an almost new jacuzzi to melt stress away. Fully fenced home for privacy, rain gutters, custom palm trees in the back with a perfectly manicured landscape. Epoxy treated garage with a 18,000lb lift and overhead storage. Located in the heart of St Cloud, close to great schools, shopping, about 20 minutes to Lake Nona, 30 minutes to airport, close to VA Hospital, 50 minutes to Cocoa Beach and cape Canaveral for the spaceship launches and less than 45 minutes to Disney and Universal attractions without the tourist impact. This home is ready ! Oh and did I mention this homes electric bill is only $18 a month ? Solar panels are paid for and included. Come see for yourself and get ready to make an offer...
